Required:
==========

1) phonon and phonon-gstreamer qml need to be installed before.
   while building phonon set -DPHONON_INSTALL_QT_EXTENSIONS_INTO_SYSTEM_QT=TRUE

2) plasma-mobile is needed in order to get features of different metadatamodel backends.

To know Plasma Media Center architecture and other related information browse through http://community.kde.org/Plasma/Plasma_Media_Center